The conversation of embracing our natural beauty is growing. 

I'm loving the results from using @hair.biology products that was formulated for me and other women who are looking for soft, full and beautiful hair at any age. 

Hair Biology Argan Oil Taming Serum absorbs weightlessly while it nourishes to strengthen against damage, add shine, and smooth ends and unruly grays. 

Discover the complete line of age-inspiring hair care products from Hair Biology and fall in love with your hair again. Now available at @shoppersbeauty 

#Hairbiology #ShowYourAge #ad

In a world that tells you to be a little smaller, a little quieter, and a lot less vibrant as you age, it becomes a bold revolution to say that I am celebrating my age and the experiences that come with it. 

I am embracing the changes, rather than fighting to get rid of them. I am finding ways to make the grey hairs more vibrant and the laugh lines more purposeful. 

I am embracing me as I am now, and I want my hair care to do the same. I’m so proud to partner with @hair.biology to help introduce their new hair care line made uniquely to work with our biology as we age and not against it. 

I absolutely love the Hair Biology Argan Oil Taming Serum - it absorbs weightlessly while nourishing my hair, plus it adds shine and smooths unruly strays. 

It’s also helped remind me to embrace my natural beauty and features – because I want to love the hair I have now. Now available in Canada and at @shoppersbeauty #HairBiology #Ad

Wishing everyone peace, love and good health this season and always

and lots of baked goods.

It’s time to wear that piece of clothing you loved, bought and then were too afraid to wear. 

A simple formula is to pair it with something you feel really comfortable in.

I bought this top last summer and love it but was afraid of “looking over the top” wearing it, so I paired it with something comfortable and familiar - jeans. 

I’m just glad this top from last August still fits 😅

Last week I had the absolute joy of celebrating the launch of a beautiful collection by Toni Fifi X Reitmans.

Original hand painted prints on dresses, playful accessories and a collection that is truly for everyone, the collab between @reitmans & @tonififi is absolute perfection and no one is more deserving of this than Toni.

While I have so many favourites from the collection (swipe to the end for that bag), it was what Toni said that was maybe why she’s one of my favourite fashion stylists, creators & friends in this industry &  why Reitmans is truly a special Canadian brand.

‘It’s not just about the beautiful collection, it’s about the acceptance of immigrants in Canada who add to the vibrant fabric of our nation. It’s about the value that women over 40 holds and it’s about the celebration & joy of Black & Brown women.’ These are Toni’s words (although not exact so please forgive me. )

Fashion can be about so much more, and this beautiful event and collection was just that.

I hope you get to see the magic of this collection for yourself.

#thismamaneedsavacay #ToniFifiXReitmans #Reitmans #canadianfashion
